CustomField.formula: IF( CONTAINS(TEXT(Intapp_Time_Total_Management__c),"Own it"), "TTM", IF( CONTAINS(TEXT(Rekoop_Time_Management__c),"Own it - Cloud"), "Rekoop", IF( ISPICKVAL(DTE_Legacy__c,"Own it"), "DTE Legacy", IF( AND( CONTAINS(TEXT(Intapp_Time_Core_Management__c),"Own it"), NOT(ISPICKVAL(Intapp_Time_Capture__c,"Own it")), NOT(ISPICKVAL(Time_Builder__c,"Own it")) ), "Core", IF( AND( OR( ISPICKVAL(DTE_Axiom__c,"Own it"), CONTAINS(TEXT(Intapp_Time_Core_Management__c),"Own it") ), OR( ISPICKVAL(Time_Builder__c,"Own it"), CONTAINS(TEXT(Intapp_Time_Capture__c),"Own it") ) ), "Possible TTM", IF( AND( OR( ISPICKVAL(DTE_Axiom_Mobile__c,"Own it"), CONTAINS(TEXT(Intapp_Time_Mobile__c),"Own it") ), OR( ISPICKVAL(Time_Builder__c,"Own it"), CONTAINS(TEXT(Intapp_Time_Capture__c),"Own it") ) ), "Capture & Mobile", IF( ISPICKVAL(Time_Builder__c,"Own it"), "Time Builder Only", IF( CONTAINS(TEXT(Intapp_Time_Capture__c),"Own it"), "Time Capture Only", IF( AND( ISPICKVAL(DTE_Axiom__c,"Own it"), OR( ISPICKVAL(DTE_Axiom_Mobile__c,"Own it"), CONTAINS(TEXT(Intapp_Time_Mobile__c),"Own it") ) ), "Possible Core", IF( ISPICKVAL(DTE_Axiom__c,"Own it"), "DTE Axiom Only", IF( OR( CONTAINS(TEXT(Intapp_Time_Mobile__c),"Own it"), ISPICKVAL(DTE_Axiom_Mobile__c,"Own it") ), "Mobile Only", IF( CONTAINS(TEXT(Intapp_Time__c),"Own it"), "Other", "Not a Time Customer" ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) )
